          <li><a href="/D1912/driving-lessons-glasgow-north" class="text-[#F8F0CB]/80 hover:text-[#E7CE50]">Glasgow North</a></li>
          <li><a href="/D1912/driving-lessons-glasgow-southside" class="text-[#F8F0CB]/80 hover:text-[#E7CE50]">Glasgow South Side</a></li>
